利用現代分子技術(DNA sequences of ''ndh''F ,cpDNA (trnL-F & psbA-trnH) and nrDNA (ITS))以及型態特徵比對，可知其與[[東風草|東風草]](''B. megacephala'')較近，基部均有木質化現象。<ref name=":14">{{Cite journal|title=Phylogenetic relationships in ''Blumea'' (Asteraceae: Inuleae)as evidenced by molecular and morphological data|author=P. Pornpongrungrueng1, F. Borchsenius1, M. Englund, A. A. Anderberg, M. H. G. Gustafsson|url=|journal=Pl Syst Evol  |issue=|doi=10.1007/s00606-007-0581-7|others=|year=2007|volume=269 |page=223–243|pmid=}}</ref><ref name=":15">{{Cite journal|title=Evolutionary relationships in the Asteraceae tribe Inuleae (incl. Plucheeae)evidenced by DNA sequences of ''ndh''F; with notes on the systematic positions of some aberrant genera|author=Arne A. Anderberg, Pia Eldena¨s, Randall J. Bayer, Markus Englund|url=|journal=Organisms, Diversity & Evolution |issue=|doi=10.1007/s00606-007-0581-7|others=|year=2005|volume=5|page=135–146|pmid=}}</ref>

